  + $ 2/8x+4/8 &= 1/8x + 12/8 \ 2x + 4 &= x + 12 \ x &= 12 - 4 \ x &= 8 $ 
  + $ 3(4x - 3) &= 2x + 1 \ 12x - 9 &= 2x + 1 \ 10x &= -8 \ x &= -0.8 $ 
